<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Récompenses du clan Werewolf Online</title>
  <meta name="description"
    content="Site web du clan Werewolf Online. Le site explique les règles, les quêtes et les évènements." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://svgsilh.com/png-1024/159979-400099.png">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="https://svgsilh.com/png-1024/159979-400099.png">
</head>

<body>
  <header id="content" class="reveal">
    <h1>
      Récompenses<br> ꧁Werewolf Online꧂
    </h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="reveal">
      <select id="menu" value={optnMenu} onChange="redirection()">
        <option value="accueil">Accueil</option>
        <option value="regles">Règles</option>
        <option value="quetes">Quêtes</option>
        <option value="recompenses" selected>Récompenses</option>
        <option value="events">Évènements</option>
        <option value="items">Items spéciaux</option>
        <option value="questionnaire">Questionnaire</option>
        <option value="search">Chercher quelqu'un</option>
        <option value="infos">Informations</option>
        <!--option value="quest-copy">Copier l'annonce de la quête</option-->
      </select>
    </section>
    <section id="bonus-malus" class="border reveal">
      <h2>Bonus/malus</h2>
      <p>
        Tous les 8000xp lors d'une quête, 1 quête <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png"> gratuite. </br>
    Moins de 300xp lors d'une quête, prochaine quête <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png"> à 800 <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png">. </br>
  Moins de 1000xp lors d'une quête, prochaine quête <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png"> à 600 <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png">.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="100kxp" class="border reveal">
      <h2>Tous les 100k xp contribué au clan</h2>
      <p>Vous pouvez choisir entre:</p>
      <p>1 quête <img class="gem" src="https://cdn.wolvesville.com/challenges/icons/challenge-gems@2x.png"> gratuite
        <br>
        3 quêtes <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png"> gratuites
        <br>
        90 <img class="roses" src="https://cdn.glitch.global/da17588f-b176-421d-842d-6ef157fe00f3/rose.png?v=1709046833983">
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="topxp" class="border reveal">
      <h2>Top XP du mois</h2>
      <p> Chaque mois la personne ayant fait le plus d’xp gagnera 2 quêtes <img class="or" src="https://www.wolvesville.com/static/media/silver_coin.7b12538367a6d2cfa2c0.png"> gratuites </p>
    </section>
    <section class="return reveal">
      <a href="#">
        <img class="returnLogo" src="https://cdn.glitch.global/da17588f-b176-421d-842d-6ef157fe00f3/fleche.png?v=1709046893508">
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="reveal">
    <a target="_blank" href="https://discord.com/invite/Yt3hM8Dck2">
      <img class="lien" src="https://cdn.glitch.global/da17588f-b176-421d-842d-6ef157fe00f3/logo%20discord.png?v=1709046892380">
    </a>
    <br>
    <a target="_blank" href="https://instagram.com/werewolfonline.clan?igshid=NTc4MTIwNjQ2YQ==">
      <img class="lien" src="https://cdn.glitch.global/da17588f-b176-421d-842d-6ef157fe00f3/logo%20insta.png?v=1709046891548">
    </a>
  </footer>
  <script src="scripts/script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>